name: Putz House Cake matted ready to frame print
description:
We've been collecting little vintage cardboard "Putz" houses forever. We actually display them year round in our home. They are a holiday classic and we think everyone can remember being a kid and assembling a tiny imaginary village beneath the tree. 
Well it was a given that we would paint a Putz house for the holidays...but we had to give it our twist. Yes, ours sits atop an adorable mini cake. This is one of our absolute fave paintings. Adorned with Starlite mints, sprinkles, and itty bitty bottle brush trees. This is a piece that not only celebrates our love for Christmas and Cake...but also the magical collectibles we grew up with. 

This is an 8 x 10 print of our original painting that is matted and ready to frame. Signed and dated, and fits an 11 x 14 frame.

name: Snowman Cake matted ready to frame print (fits 11x14 frame)
description:
We had a goal in mind when we painted this cake. We said "Let's make this the cheeriest holiday cake ever!" And we think we just may have succeeded! Of all the paintings that we do our absolute faves are our holiday themed sweets. We just love the idea of capturing a tiny magical world and loads of holiday spirit atop a cake. And we think the color scheme is perfect...a melding of our pastel color palette and the classic red and green of traditional Christmas. Complete with a cheerful snowman, his cotton tailed friend, a sprinkling of jimmies, and starlite mints.

This is an 8 x 10 print of our original painting that is matted and ready to frame. Signed and dated, and fits an 11 x 14 frame.

name: Christmas Cupcakes matted ready to frame print
description:
Christmas Cupcakes are so festive that it's impossible not to get utterly overcome by the Christmas spirit by just taking a single glance at them. We love switching up the classic Christmas color palette...because aren't pastels just so magical!? We used some of our very own vintage cupcake toppers as models when we painted this still life. The snowman is our fave...or maybe the tiny shiny brite...or maybe the bottle brush tree... :)
 If you collect our pieces year round this is a must to round our your holiday cupcakes collection.

This is an 8 x 10 print of our original painting that is matted and ready to frame. Signed, dated, and fits an 11 x 14 frame.

name: Vintage inspired Bottle Brush Tree ornament
description:
The second we listed our vintage Putz House Christmas ornies we received so many requests for a handmade ornament featuring one of our original Christmas bottlebrush trees. Well we just so happened to already have one in the works…and here it is! We made it slightly larger so that it really stands out! It measures 6 ½ inches tall and with the fine dusting of clear glitter it simply looks magical.
Vintage bottlebrush trees can be found in just about every room of our home…all year round! They are one of our favorite collectibles and they always succeed in bringing some festive magic to our surroundings. 
A high quality print of our original painting mounted on study mat board that we back with some vintagey sheet music. It hangs by our signature baker’s twine and is signed, dated, and sealed for protection.

So we made these on the double, and now we're thrilled to share them with all of you. They're made of sturdy mat board that we hand cut, and then sand the edges smooth. Each is backed with vintage recipe book clippings with corresponding cupcake recipes to match each cupcake! And of course...for some added holiday magic we've given them a fine dusting of Glitter! They hang by a loop of classic bakers twine. 
And don't limit these cuties to the Christmas tree...these are fab additions to tie onto a gift for the cupcake lover in your life. Or display them year round on cabinet knobs, drawer pulls, or even hang them from a chandelier.  
Set of four, glittered, signed & dated, sealed for protection. Each cupcake measures approximately 3 1/2 inches wide.

name: Apple Pie a la mode matted ready to frame print (fits 11 x 14 frame)
description:
Apple Pie A La Mode

8x10 matted print (fits 11x14 frame)

After years of feeding our Cupcake addiction we had to finally come out publicly about our love affair with pie. In some places it's a matter of choosing sides...Are you a Cake/Cupcake fan? or are you a Pie fan?

Well, we could never ever choose. Our minds are much broader and we are simply SWEETS fans. When painting Apple Pie our first artistic choice was to go VINTAGE...because it's just an American classic...it's Holidays and it's Grandma's house. So right away we painted a background of the ultimate vintage wallpaper in our favorite color scheme of tan, cream, pink, aqua...and of course, we had to go "a la mode!" If you look closely you can see the vanilla beans in the ice cream. The pic totally does not do this painting justice...the details are fab.

This is a high quality print of our original painting. It's matted and ready to frame in a sturdy professional quality mat. The artwork measures 8" x 10" and the mat fits in an 11" x 14" frame. All of our matted prints are titled, signed, & dated...and they come in a protective cellophane sleeve.

Check our other listings for different size prints and /or versions that are mounted on canvas or wooden plaques. Also, if you remember seeing a painting of ours and you're not seeing it now...by all means...send us an email and we can find it for you and/or do a custom piece for you right away!

We ship WORLDWIDE  just message us! :)

name: A Wise Woman Knows Her Baking Scrapbook kit
description:
A Wise Woman Knows Her Baking Scrapbook kit

We are so excited about this kit! Because not only did we get awesome feedback from our students about how fun it was to make…but we’re also donating a percentage of the proceeds to Operation Stars and Stripes. We were so thrilled to be part of the Sweethearts on the Homefront event in Atlanta GA, and we wanted to pay it forward even further. 
The inspiration for the kit came from the event itself, which honored what it is to be a patriot back home. Canning, conserving during wartime, and continuing the tradition of family recipes that are passed down through generations. With a 1940’s style gal on the cover and lots of sweet imagery throughout. Keep this binder as your own personal recipe book or even as a sweets themed scrapbook for family memories.
The kit includes chipboard covers, mat board pages, binder rings, tons of our original artwork, ribbons, and glitter. All you’ll need is scissors, a couple paint brushes, some decoupage medium such as mod podge, and a standard hole punch. This kit is tried and true and our students absolutely loved it. Check out the hashtag #sweetheartsonthehomefront on Instagram to see some glimpses of this kit in action.

book measures 8x10

name: Vintage inspired Cupcake with bottle brush tree ornament
description:
Ok, if you combine a Christmas cupcake with a vintage bottlebrush tree it just might qualify for sweetness overload. We love our Holiday collections…and we love making art that is based on our favorite Holiday collectibles. That’s what we love about our handmade Christmas ornaments…they are inspired by our collections…and then we actually make them into all new collectibles. The whole process comes full circle. And this one is totally at the top of our favorites list…seriously, a bottlebrush tree sitting atop a sweet holiday cupcake! Love it!
This one measures 6 inches tall and of course…it’s got a fab dusting of clear glitter. Made from a high quality print of our original painting that’s mounted on sturdy mat board, and the back is covered with some vintagey sheet music. name: Halloween Cupcakes matted ready to frame print
description:
Halloween, as far as Holidays go, easily ranks as THE most fun of all. The Halloween spirit is certainly infectious…first a single house is decorated, and within a week the entire neighborhood is strewn with faux cobwebs and bedsheet ghouls. Besides the traditional Tricks and Treats we’ve always been taken in by the “edible art” that bakers craft for this festive day. It seems that Halloween cupcakes are taken to new levels of fun and creativity each year. And over-the-top theme cakes are now a necessity. Sweets adorned with vintage style plastic toppers, sprinkles in festive colors, and seasonal candies as decorations. 
Our Halloween Cupcakes painting is a tribute to the Spooky & Sweet traditions of one of our favorite days of the year! 
This high quality print comes matted and ready to frame. 8 x 10 print within an 11 x 14 mat. Signed & dated.

Happy Fall! 
xo, J & A

Kit contains:

Super detailed instructions, tips and tricks
Step by Step photos
Stretched, raised canvas
Tracing paper
Our original line drawings ( 2 to choose from!)
Pretty patterned papers


**All you will need to gather is:

Scissors
Mod Podge, or Gel Medium
A pencil
Paint brushes
Black craft paint


As with any of our kits..we are only an email away! If you have any questions or need a little advice we are here for you! :)

description:
Gorgeous Gal
8x10 matted print fits 11x14 frame
(pink)

Our Gorgeous Gals are our brand new design...but they're based upon some paintings that we made over a decade ago. Back then we came across some old antique white peeling paint cupboard doors...and they served as THE perfect canvases for our "Ladies" ...just simple black line paintings of beautiful retro gals, reminiscent of 40's pin-up and ad gals from the Golden Age. Well, we painted our "Ladies" on those old doors, hung them up in our store and they sold out quicker than we could even imagine.
 So now, fast forward a decade or more...we brought our "ladies" back...but now we call them our "gorgeous gals"...and we updated them with our with love for color, pattern, and paper collage. That's our starting point...a highly textured, super antiquey collage...the photos do not do our gals justice. The collage backdrop really has a great vintagey feel. And then we paint our gals with sleek black lines...using color only for their lipstick! We have two color versions of our Gorgeous Gals...Pink or Blue. So check back if you're finding one and not the other...OR by all means, shoot us an email and we can make one custom on the double!

This is a high quality print of our original painting. It's matted and ready to frame in a sturdy professional quality mat. The artwork measures 8" x 10" and the mat fits in an 11" x 14" frame. All of our matted prints are titled, signed, & dated...and they come in a protective cellophane sleeve.

Check our other listings for different size prints and /or versions that are mounted on canvas or wooden plaques. Also, if you remember seeing a painting of ours and you're not seeing it now...by all means...send us an email and we can find it for you and/or do a custom piece for you right away!

Allie & Amy look fantastic and nothing is lost in the details of the background textures and effects...such as the paint crackling, glazing, paint spatter, etc...
To fit the dimensions of this print and our other size mats we pulled the focus in closer on the girls faces and the oh-so-essential sweets in hand!
This is the perfect piece for sisters, best friends...and your favorite "partner in crime"...you know you have one! : )

name: classic buttercream frosted cupcake green mini print
description:
For us it all started with the classic buttercream frosted cupcake. When we had our brick & mortar retail location in Jersey...after a long day's work we'd hop in our van and make the hour drive into NYC just to get a box of cupcakes from our favorite bakery.
